<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="personally-adv">personally <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'pɜːsənəli/    美 /'pɜːrsənəli/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-in-person">1.★ <strong>亲自 (in person)；个别地：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>In it were photos of all the actors of our show, personally signed by each performer.
里面有我们节目中每位演员亲笔签名的照片。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>[句子副词] 就个人而言：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I personally advise you to learn some basic Chinese in order to communicate with local people.
我个人建议你学一些基本的汉语，以便和当地人沟通。</p><footer>2014 天津书面表达</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Personally, I prefer to work in a team.
就我个人而言，我更喜欢在团队里工作。</p><footer>2008 浙江书面表达</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>They gave money to the old people’s home either <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (personal) or through their companies.  （2015 安徽改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. personally  </p></div>